    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban advertising and sale of domestic pets online",
        "additional_details": "Too many people advertise and sell domestic pets, some of which are unhealthy or even stolen, online.\r\n \r\nWe believe it is time this avenue was blocked off\r\n \r\nDogs, puppies, cats and kittens are advertised and sold on many websites, with little regulation.\r\n \r\nSome pets that are sold on these internet sites are either stolen, have already changed hands many times, or come from abroad.\r\n \r\nThe Government needs to shut down all avenues to unscrupulous, breeder/dealers.\r\n \r\nThe ban on third-party sales of dogs and cats under six months has not stopped people advertising and selling pets online. More needs to be done.",
